# Blender MCP + BIM Workflow

- For scene, viewport, and IFC/Bonsai tasks in this workspace, call Blender MCP tools first.
- Follow the session guidance in [workspace_config/guidelines.md](file:///home/lfn/projetos_bim/workspace_config/guidelines.md).
- **Before MCP investigation or CAD Sketcher / slab profile work**, read [agents/knowledge/](file:///home/lfn/projetos_bim/blender_mcp/agents/knowledge/README.md) or apply [.cursor/rules/blender_mcp_agent_knowledge.mdc](file:///home/lfn/projetos_bim/blender_mcp/.cursor/rules/blender_mcp_agent_knowledge.mdc).
